cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.SY

The paper deals with vision-based autonomous driving, which is a problem in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). It also involves robotics (cs.RO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as the autonomous system needs to perceive the world and act in it. Additionally, the paper discusses the reduction of infractions, which is related to control systems (cs.SY).
